[?2004l[?2004h> Steps
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 1) Generate the WAV in `/app/audioproc.py`:
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Mono, 16 kHz, exactly 3.0 seconds.
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Signal = sum of 5 sines at [220, 330, 440, 550, 660] Hz.
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Add uniform dither in (-1e-4, 1e-4).
[?2004l[?2004h>    - RMS-normalize the dithered signal to 0.2 ± 0.002.
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Normalize before 16-bit quantization, then save `/app/data/clip.wav` (PCM int16).
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 2) Compute the STFT using scipy and write `/app/data/mag.csv`:
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Use `scipy.signal.stft` with parameters: `fs=16000`, `nperseg=1024`, `noverlap=768`, `nfft=1024`, `window='"'"'hann'"'"'`, `boundary=None`, `padded=False`, `return_onesided=True`.
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Export linear magnitude (not dB) to CSV with schema `frame,bin,val` (one row per bin per frame).
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 3) Use awk (mawk or gawk) to produce `/app/data/peaks.csv`:
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Create `/app/data/peaks.csv` with columns `frame,f1_bin,f2_bin,f3_bin` (one row per frame, 0-indexed).
[?2004l[?2004h>    - For each frame, f1/f2/f3 must be the true top-3 magnitude bins in descending order (f1 ≥ f2 ≥ f3).
[?2004l[?2004h>    - Provide a Bash script at `/app/solution.sh` that orchestrates the pipeline and is responsible for generating `data/peaks.csv` using awk.
[?2004l[?2004h>    - The script must support `PEAKS_ONLY=1`: when set, read `/app/data/mag.csv`, generate `/app/data/peaks.csv` via awk, and exit without running other steps. M[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[C[K.
